headline: Dover Expands Offering of Hygienic Pumps
summary: Dover Corporation (NYSE: DOV) today announced that it has acquired ipp Pump Products GmbH ("ipp"), which is now part of the Pump Solutions Group ("PSG") business unit within Dover's Pumps & Process Solutions segment.
